        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Ellen Grove property values are driven by estate presentation quality, block size and proximity to Forest Lake's retail hub and the Ipswich Motorway. Modern estate homes on flat usable blocks in tidy streets consistently outperform older or constrained sites. Young families buying here compare directly against Durack and Richlands, so accurate price positioning relative to those corridors is essential.</p>
