          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Well-priced Ellen Grove homes typically sell within 28 to 45 days. The suburb draws a consistent buyer pool of young families and first home buyers active across the outer western corridor. Properties that are accurately priced and well presented attract inquiry within the first two weeks of a well-run campaign.</p>
