        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Ellen Grove has a relaxed outer suburban character with modern estate streets, parks and convenient access to Forest Lake's shopping and services. Families are drawn by the combination of newer housing stock, practical motorway access and a price point that delivers more space than comparable inner suburban budgets.</p>
